name: Branching Out
description:
Branching Out is a community app aimed to connect plant lovers of all experience levels. The app, created during the UW WINFO Hackathon of 2022, "embraces the new" by helping people improve the most popular pandemic hobby - taking care of plants! Users can add plants they are taking care of, learn how to take care of it, and be connected to others taking care of that same plant. Users can also sell their gardening products and plants through the Market feature.
